high_descs: Turn around completely, walk to the wall, then turn right to face the toilet.
Pick up the sponge that is on the back of the toilet.
Turn to the right, walk forward a few steps, then turn left to face the bathroom sink.
Rinse the sponge off in the sink before taking it back out again.
Move back from the sink a bit and to the right to face the bathroom cabinets to the right of the sink.
Place the sponge in the lower left bathroom cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a wet sponge in a bathroom cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the toilet.
Pick up the sponge off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and pick the sponge back up.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right and take two step forward, turn around to face the counter and look down at the cabinets.
Open the second lower cabinet door from the right and put the clean sponge inside, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the sponge from the top of the toilet.
Turn right and walk forward past the toilet, then turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out.
Move slightly to the right and backwards away from the sink.
Put the sponge in the bottom cabinet second from the right, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge in a cabinet.
